narrative_summary: - Invoked the `dagster-expert` skill to get Dagster-specific guidance and reference files
- Read the integrations index and dbt-specific reference files to find the correct scaffolding approach for a remote GitHub-hosted dbt project
- Used `uv add dagster-dbt` to install the dagster-dbt integration package

- Ran `uv run dg scaffold defs dagster_dbt.DbtProjectComponent acme_dbt --git-url https://github.com/dagster-io/jaffle_shop` to create the component, generating a `defs.yaml` in `src/acme_co_dataeng/defs/acme_dbt/`
- Fetched the `profiles.yml` from the jaffle_shop GitHub repo to identify the required dbt adapter (DuckDB)
- Ran `uv run dg list defs` to verify the component loaded correctly, confirming 8 dbt assets (seeds, staging models, mart models) and 20 asset checks were registered successfully
